      "text": "\"\nUSER PROMPT:\ncheck issue 113, respond to any comments\n\nINSTRUCTIONS:\nCreate a list of tasks that are required to resolve the user prompt\nFor each task, provide the CLI command required to interface with the system\n\nOUTPUT:\nProvide your outputs as JSON that can be parsed programatically\n\nEXAMPLE:\n...\n\"",
