      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Goal\n- create an interface that facilitates software\ndevelopment\n\nUse case\n- building fun projects quickly thanks to AI assistance\n\n(v1)\n\nFunctional Requirements \n- multiple users\n- \"free mode\" uses all open-source tooling\n- easy to use interface\n- can store past chats (history)\n- can parse codebases for context\n- can perform all typical software eng tasks\n    - design\n    - code\n    - test\n\nNon-Functional Requirements\n- can handle 4 users simultaneously\n- <100ms response latency (even if \"thinking...\")\n- manipulate files\n- interface with GitHub\n- map model size to compute capability\n- interface with client & server file system\n- can load full repo into server-side vector db for\nRAG\n\nSystem Logic Flow\nUser prompt\n<--> send & receive text\n    \n    LLM-powered system \n        <--> GitHub\n        <--> File System\n\nExample Interface\n",
      "fontSize": 39.07572537440753,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Goal\n- create an interface that facilitates software development\n\nUse case\n- building fun projects quickly thanks to AI assistance\n\n(v1)\n\nFunctional Requirements \n- multiple users\n- \"free mode\" uses all open-source tooling\n- easy to use interface\n- can store past chats (history)\n- can parse codebases for context\n- can perform all typical software eng tasks\n    - design\n    - code\n    - test\n\nNon-Functional Requirements\n- can handle 4 users simultaneously\n- <100ms response latency (even if \"thinking...\")\n- manipulate files\n- interface with GitHub\n- map model size to compute capability\n- interface with client & server file system\n- can load full repo into server-side vector db for RAG\n\nSystem Logic Flow\nUser prompt\n<--> send & receive text\n    \n    LLM-powered system \n        <--> GitHub\n        <--> File System\n\nExample Interface\n",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    }
